It is probably because you make an AJAX call (getAllCustomer) in your componentDidMount method. If the response arrives while your component is unmounted, the setState in the resolve callback will cause the React warning. You should better cancel all ongoing AJAX call in the component&#39;s componentWillUnmount method. You can do this with Axios : [https://github.com/axios/axios#cancellation][1]

